Tweaked for Multiple Monitors, Chatbox from Advanced Peripherials and CC:Tweaked Speaker and Redstone Relay usages..

Setup:
Within Colony boundaries:
Wired modems for all peripherals below
- At least 2 advanced monitors (4x4)
- Advanced computer + chest + mebridge respectively
- Speaker + Chat box + Redstone Relay with a redstone lamp on top of it
- ae2 storage system should be connected to bridge 

files should be placed in saves/computercraft/idfolder/
and run main.lua file

ALL THE MODS 10 
neoforge : 21.1.191
